parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Front Passenger Seat Occupancy Sensor Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front passenger seat occupancy sensor can cause the passenger airbag to malfunction, leading to potential injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger airbag off light is illuminated
the restraint system malfunction warning message appears
the sensor reports an occupant when the seat is empty

the recall notification has been received
but the repair is delayed or unavailable.
